text: Ate alaha ne hareka jivanadhari nu pani tom paida kita, phira inham vicom ko'i apane peta de bhara calada hai. Ate inham vicom ko'i do pairam te calada hai. Ate inham vicom ko'i cara pairam te calada hai. Alaha jo cahuda hai paida karada hai. Niresadeha alaha hara ciza di samaratha rakhada hai
